{"tid":1616347,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"禁蒙面法點樣化解？ How to Overcome Anti-Mask Law ?By Chapman Chen","createTime":"2019-10-03T11:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T11:34:27.000Z","uid":276301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"008421f6b6d1d1355c5a4ea45873e43bcfdc0304","tid":1616347,"uid":276301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RWac1DR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRWac1DR.jpg&h=8eaf1529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n禁蒙面法點樣化解？ How to Overcome Anti-Mask Law? By Chapman Chen曾焯文, HKBNews<br />\n據多家傳媒消息，行會周五召開特別會，擬引《緊急法》立「禁蒙面法」，對付示威者。民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆、連同警隊員佐級協會前主席陳祖光等今日宣布成立「禁蒙面法推動組」。日本郊區有間細公司，創辦人北川修可根據高清相片、三D面容數據，用樹脂塑膠，度身訂造仿真度極高面具，每個售日元三十萬（港幣二萬），叫價不菲  。（北川修在某印刷機製造廠工作時，度出這條橋。）<br />\n<br />\n此外，美國概念畫家Leo Selvaggio根據自己面容，用三D打印技術，製造樹脂面具，包頭髮膚色肌理，相當迫真，不易惹人生疑，售價連運費包裝，約港幣二千。但只有一個樣，就係Selvaggio本人，如果好多人同時戴，一樣會被人識穿而被捕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z6UEGD0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz6UEGD0.jpg&h=b3686aea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最平靚正的方法都係回歸傳統，濃妝艷抹，尤其是粵劇生、旦、淨、末、丑面譜，玩下手連阿媽都唔認得。禁蒙面法照計只禁戴面具，無禁化妝。（本文並非廣告）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XejJoSw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXejJoSw.jpg&h=691477fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFb link: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkongbilingualnews/posts/783533825417717?__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkongbilingualnews%2Fposts%2F783533825417717%3F__tn__%3D-R&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEjQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=57adb47c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkongbilingualnews/posts/783533825417717?__tn__=-R</a><br />\n<br />\nWeb link: <a href=\"https://www.hkbnews.net/post/%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%AF%E5%8C%96%E8%A7%A3%E4%B9%8E%EF%BC%9F-can-anti-mask-law-be-overcome-by-ch